Cloneable
public class DbfNumericField
extends DbfField
implements Cloneable

This class mananges dBASE Numeric fields. This field type returns the following object types as output:

  • java.lang.Double (when DbfField.getNumDec() > 0)
  • java.lang.Long (when DbfField.getNumDec() == 0)
  • com.esri.mo2.file.shp.DbfNullValue

This field type accepts the following object types as input regardless of the field's number of decimal places:

  • java.lang.Byte
  • java.lang.Double
  • java.lang.Float
  • java.lang.Integer
  • java.lang.Long
  • java.lang.Short
  • com.esri.mo2.file.shp.DbfNullValue

The default value for this field type is zero.
